</ul>=20
<div style=3D"clear:both"></div>


<h2>Derivatives (Differential Calculus)</h2>=20

<p>The Derivative is the "rate of change" or slope of a function.</p>=20
<p class=3D"floatLt"><img src=3D"https://www.mathsisfun.com/calculus/images=
/slope-x2-2.svg" alt=3D"slope x^2 at 2 has slope 4" height=3D"206" width=3D=
"165"></p>=20
