<h2>Differential Equations</h2>=20

<p>In our world things change, and <b>describing how they change</b> often =
ends up as a Differential Equation: an equation with a <b>function</b> and =
one or more of its <b>derivatives</b>:</p>=20
<p class=3D"floatRt"><img src=3D"https://www.mathsisfun.com/calculus/images=
/diff-eq-1.svg" alt=3D"" differential"=3D"" height=3D"123" width=3D"188">=
=3D 5x" height=3D"123" width=3D"188"&gt;</p>=20
